Ricardo clicks on the shoes size filter
Then The total search results  should be a string containing 'Shoes'
Then The number of filters should be (2)
Then The Filter [filterName=Brand, filterKey=Puma] should be applied
Then The Filter [filterName=shoes size, filterKey=10] should be applied
